36#include <config.h>
37
38#include <krb5/parse_units.h>
39#include <krb5/parse_time.h>
40
41static struct units time_units[] = {
42 {"year", 365 * 24 * 60 * 60},
43 {"month", 30 * 24 * 60 * 60},
44 {"week", 7 * 24 * 60 * 60},
45 {"day", 24 * 60 * 60},
46 {"hour", 60 * 60},
47 {"h", 60 * 60},
48 {"minute", 60},
49 {"m", 60},
50 {"second", 1},
51 {"s", 1},
52 {NULL, 0},
53};
54
55ROKEN_LIB_FUNCTION int ROKEN_LIB_CALL
56parse_time (const char *s, const char *def_unit)
57{
58 return parse_units (s, time_units, def_unit);
59}
60
61ROKEN_LIB_FUNCTION size_t ROKEN_LIB_CALL
62unparse_time (int t, char *s, size_t len)
63{
64 return unparse_units (t, time_units, s, len);
65}
66
67ROKEN_LIB_FUNCTION size_t ROKEN_LIB_CALL
68unparse_time_approx (int t, char *s, size_t len)
69{
70 return unparse_units_approx (t, time_units, s, len);
71}
72
73ROKEN_LIB_FUNCTION void ROKEN_LIB_CALL
74print_time_table (FILE *f)
75{
76 print_units_table (time_units, f);
77}
